    <div class="main review-item" id="4980808">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4980808/" class="title-link">大棋局与大智慧</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4980808"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/36756682/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u36756682-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/36756682/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">留给历史</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-06-08"
      class="main-meta">2011-06-08 00:01:10</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4980808_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      《时寒冰说：经济大棋局，我们怎么办》是一部窥透世界大棋局的智慧之作，也是一部还原真相，普及常识的启蒙之作，时寒冰在书中淋漓尽致的演绎了他的利益与趋势分析法。       赵汀阳说，思想的主体部分虽然是知识，但思想的奠基部分却是智慧，尽管我们无法保证那些代表智慧...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4980808/#comments">(8回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">37有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4980808_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4980808_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5022481">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5022481/" class="title-link">公开的棋局：美元、石油、粮食</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5022481"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/biechudelily/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1045015-160.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/biechudelily/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">靜</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-07-13"
      class="main-meta">2011-07-13 19:01:25</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5022481_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  <p class="main-title-tip">
                    这篇书评可能有关键情节透露
